    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>&quot;Recycle Factory Simulator&quot; is a first-person simulator game where you work in your own recycle factory.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/474302abb196022363d4d29d98f24494.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy junk, materials and machines from your in-game computer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/780617eb4412e3117d0f651e087cb566.poster.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/780617eb4412e3117d0f651e087cb566.webm?t=1727610641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/da6ad2c9ec27fd74a6a0f8f519d9ac00.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decomposite junk to seperate them into materials. Process the materials to increase their value.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/ea46b1fb73d22ab545450dfd1fa7e3ab.poster.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/ea46b1fb73d22ab545450dfd1fa7e3ab.webm?t=1727610641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/8bfea9d0212fef6d825b2b4b93d8bf19.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell the products to earn money and make profit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/5d05812681892af6f802ab0ee17b66e7.poster.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/5d05812681892af6f802ab0ee17b66e7.webm?t=1727610641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/2c95c77604b9fd76874c6f97c0a08286.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your factory and machines, pay your bills, and enjoy the game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/49ab6ed28553999fba5cd82dd00d62e3.poster.avif?t=1727610641\" width=616 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196810/extras/49ab6ed28553999fba5cd82dd00d62e3.webm?t=1727610641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is being developed by Knight Games, a solo game developer. You can follow on X for updates and other upcoming games!</i></p>",
